(383, 1383, 'Jennifer', 'Jennifer@gmail.com', '', '1.54.77.230', '2022-06-13 02:36:03', '2022-06-13 02:36:03', 'Excellent, probably the best yet.\r\nThis was an amazing trip. Totally fell in love with Vietnam, We did so much in such in two weeks. The cycling, somehow. only felt like a small part of the experience as there were so many other things that we did. Each day was full on, exceptionally well organised, great food, etc Been on a few cycle trips, and I think this was the best one so far', 0, '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/102.0.0.0 Safari/537.36', 'st_reviews', 0, 9),
